何見解？（10 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "54412245620c", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114160", "c": "127", "s": "0518", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "政府採購法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員升官等考試、114年關務人員升官等考試、114年交通事業郵政人員升資考試、114年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-bd450684-moex-00005', 'promotion-bd450684', 'promotion-bd450684-moex-114-7aee8e3e', 'sub-promotion-bd450684-02', NULL, 'essay', '依政府採購法第25 條規定，機關得視個別採購之特性，於招標文件中規
